<item>
            <title>[LU-8755] kernel update [SLES12 SP1 3.12.62-60.64.8]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8755</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The SUSE Linux Enterprise 12 SP1 kernel was updated to fix two issues.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This security bug was fixed:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;CVE-2016-5195: Local privilege escalation using MAP_PRIVATE. It is reportedly exploited in the wild (bsc#1004418).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;This non-security bug was fixed:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;sched/core: Fix a race between try_to_wake_up() and a woken up task (bsc#1002165, bsc#1001419).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
